.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, mechanic, police-officer, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, pall-mall, oliveros, bolivar
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the fisherman##1
 3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the pall-mall-smoker##1
 6. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the police-officer##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the fisherman is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the mechanic is between the bongani-smoker and the teacher##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Job           | fisherman  | teacher | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Cigar           | pall-mall       | bolivar    | oliveros      | bongani           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

