.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, freelancer, librarian, paramedic
4 different pets are kept: hamster, cat, horse, hedgehog
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cricket, cycling, sailing
1. the owner of the hamster is between the person who's sport is sailing and the owner of the horse##2
2. the freelancer is between the owner of the hamster and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the person who's sport is cricket and the dutch##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the cat is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
| Pet   | cat      | hedgehog       | hamster     | horse      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| Sport         | cycling   | sailing    | climbing | cricket   |

