.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-9::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, lettuce, spinach, tomato
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, aconite, amaryllis, iris
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, house, indie, metal
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, parkour, volleyball
 1. the person eating lettuce is the person who growsamaryllis##1
 2. the person eating tomato is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person who growsamaryllis is the person who's sport is handball##1
 4. the person eating spinach is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
 5. the fan of metal is the person eating grapefruit##1
 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the person who growstulip is between the person who growsiris and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
| Flower           | iris | tulip | aconite   | amaryllis |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | folk       | metal      | house     |
| Sport         | parkour       | volleyball | cycling    | handball  |

