 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the person who's sport is skiing is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is soccer##2
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's sport is skiing and the person who's sport is soccer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda    | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
